fields.name: Wooden Dining Table
fields.description: Beautiful wooden dining table suitable for 6 persons. This elegant dining table will be a perfect addition to your dining room, bringing warmth and style to your home.

fields.name: Leather Sofa
fields.description: Comfortable leather sofa with reclining seats. Sink into luxury and relaxation with this premium leather sofa. Perfect for movie nights and cozy evenings at home.

fields.name: LED Smart TV
fields.description: 55-inch LED Smart TV with Ultra HD resolution. Immerse yourself in stunning visuals and crystal-clear sound with this cutting-edge smart TV. Elevate your entertainment experience.

fields.name: Queen Bed
fields.description: Elegant queen-sized bed with upholstered headboard. Create a luxurious bedroom retreat with this stylish and comfortable queen bed. Perfect for a restful night's sleep.

fields.name: Kitchen Mixer
fields.description: High-performance kitchen mixer with multiple attachments. Take your culinary skills to the next level with this versatile kitchen mixer. Effortlessly prepare delicious meals and baked goods.

fields.name: Laptop
fields.description: Thin and lightweight laptop with powerful performance. Stay productive on the go with this sleek and powerful laptop. Ideal for work, entertainment, and everyday computing tasks.

fields.name: Coffee Table
fields.description: Modern coffee table with tempered glass top. Add a touch of contemporary style to your living room with this chic coffee table. Perfect for serving drinks, displaying decor, and more.

fields.name: Washing Machine
fields.description: Front-loading washing machine with energy-efficient features. Make laundry day a breeze with this efficient and reliable washing machine. Keep your clothes clean and fresh with ease.

fields.name: Desk Chair
fields.description: Ergonomic desk chair with adjustable armrests. Stay comfortable and focused during long work sessions with this ergonomic desk chair. Customize your seating experience for optimal support and comfort.

fields.name: Smart speaker Yandex Station Max
fields.description: Smart speaker Yandex Station Max with voice assistant Alice, supports Zigbee communication protocol. It is presented in graphite color, 65 W sound power, wireless Wi-Fi (2.4-5 GHz) and Bluetooth 4.2 and the ability to be integrated into the Smart Home ecosystem from an official supplier with a manufacturer’s warranty.

fields.name: High floor rack
fields.description: A high rack is a multifunctional storage system for home and garden that will help you effectively use every centimeter of space.

fields.name: Immersion blender
fields.description: Powerful kitchen processor with metal removable blender. 2 speed modes for liquid and viscous products, as well as smooth speed control to prevent mixture splashing and smooth transition to the optimal speed.

fields.name: Toaster Kitfort KT-2047 (KT-2047)
fields.description: The Kitfort KT-2047 toaster is designed for those who love to enjoy aromatic and crispy toasted bread. The special taste and color of toast is obtained due to the caramelization of the sugar contained in the flour during the cooking process.

fields.name: Apple Smartphone iPhone 13
fields.description: Экран: OLED Super Retina XDR, 6.1" (2532x1170), Процессор: Apple A15 Bionic; Память: оперативная 4 ГБ, встроенная 128 ГБ, Поддержка сетей: 2G/3G/4G (LTE)/5G; Размеры (ШхВхТ): 71.5 х 146.7 х 7.65 мм;

fields.name: Corner sofa
fields.description: Thanks to its design, the sofa will look perfect in any interior. A deep seat, an inclined back along the entire length of the sofa, and a practical table will allow you to comfortably spend time on the sofa, be it reading books, watching TV or just relaxing with the whole family.

fields.name: Apple AirPods Pro headphones (2nd gen)
fields.description: The 2nd generation Apple AirPods Pro headphones have been redesigned for even richer sound. Next-level Active Noise Canceling and Adaptive Transparency reduce more ambient noise. Spatial audio takes immersion to a completely personal level.

fields.name: Hob Bosch PKF375FP2E
fields.description: Glass-ceramic hob with a width of 30 cm: convenient for both cooking and cleaning. Intuitive DirectSelect control: allows you to set the power of the burner or activate additional functions with one click.

fields.name: Apple Watch Series 9 GPS
fields.description: The Apple Watch Series 9 GPS 45mm Starlight Aluminum Sport smartwatch features a Retina LTPO OLED touchscreen with a high brightness of 2000 nits, making information easy to read even in direct sunlight.

fields.name: Microwave oven CASO MCG 25
fields.description: Microwave oven CASO MCG 25 Ceramic Chef with flat ceramic bottom. The device operates in a combined mode (microwaves and convection), which allows you to cook food quickly and evenly.
